# Bug Prioritization

Not all bugs are equally important.

### 🔴 Critical

```text
App crashes

↓

Users cannot login

↓

Reports disappear

↓

AI not working
```

Fix these immediately.

---

### 🟡 Medium

```text
Typo

↓

Slow loading

↓

Incorrect icon
```

Fix in the next update.

---

### 🟢 Low

```text
Minor UI improvement

↓

Animation issue

↓

Theme suggestion
```

Can wait.

---

# Feature Requests

Users will always ask for new features.

Example:

```text
Doctor Sharing

↓

Apple Health

↓

Google Fit

↓

More Languages

↓

Dark Mode
```

Don't build everything immediately.

Ask yourself:

**Will this help most users?**

If not, save it for later.

